Click on 'Add Coverage'

1. Click on paddock areas to add coverage
 ![Tracmap Add Coverage](addCoverage.png "Tracmap Add Coverage" )
2. Treatment total (Top left)
3. Click 'Products' (Left side)

 Add Product
1. Enter product name
2. Enter rate

![Tracmap Add Products](addProducts.png "Tracmap Add Products" )

 Estimated product total
![Tracmap Product total](productTotal.png "Tracmap Product Total" )

1. Enter estimated product total
2. Click 'Calculate Rate'

 Application Rate
![Tracmap Application Rate](applicationRate.png "Tracmap Application Rate" )

1. The rate is then locked in
2. Click 'Submit'
3. Click 'Confirm'
4. Create another order or return to the last screen